**Bonus income is fully taxable** — it is added to your salary and taxed at your applicable marginal slab rate. Unlike regular salary where TDS is spread across the year, bonuses attract TDS in the month they are paid. This calculator helps you estimate the exact TDS on your bonus and the net amount you will actually receive.
